Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.util.delayedinput

Class DelayedInputRequest<T>

java.lang.Object
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.util.delayedinput.DelayedInputRequest<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of data to request.
Direct Known Subclasses:
DelayedCommandInputRequest, DelayedStructureSpecificationInputRequest
public class DelayedInputRequest<T> extends Object
Represents a request for delayed input. E.g. by waiting for user input.

  • Method Details

    • cancel

      public final void cancel()
      Cancels the request if it is still waiting for input.

      Calling this method after the request has already completed has no effect.

      See completed().

    • set

      See completed().

      Parameters:

    • cleanup

      protected void cleanup()
